## [self-replicating media](scrolls/selfreplicatingmedia)

# Trash Magic
 
- the purpose is to replicate things made from trash
- when everyone in the world has the same trash, all we need to replicate free things is information
- we encode information in trash using trash which replicates things made from trash
- "magic" refers to the spark of desire to replicate a thing which jumps from one person to the next, it forms the basis of all religion and marketing